{"tid":1663702,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"Ways to stand with Hong Kong","createTime":"2019-10-19T14:37:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T19:01:42.000Z","uid":121409,"like":80,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"4ff27302ba976568609ec559d63ee5a681cc6911","tid":1663702,"uid":121409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T14:37:33.000Z","msg":"Knowing some of the foreigners are paying attention to Hong Kong protest but don't know how could they stand with Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\nWith discussion in this forum, I summarized some actions that everyone could do to show their support to HK.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TT5SbnG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTT5SbnG.jpg&h=ad171207&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/19/181031_55b89ce8c626c051166e4f5de42c2c5e.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F19%2F181031_55b89ce8c626c051166e4f5de42c2c5e.PNG&h=4eb3b875&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j9Nxbqc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj9Nxbqc.jpg&h=7aa57576&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9eCk4Lg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9eCk4Lg.jpg&h=f47a69ee&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aNhxbri.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaNhxbri.jpg&h=ad5b6a52&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPlease help share it with your friends if you find it is useful.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nThank you for supporting us and being one of us as a freedom fighter<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a56a99fa6